<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">We have talked about this before, but the most=
 important job for any sort of adviser to the target company in any sort of=
 hostile mergers-and-acquisitions situation is to=C2=A0<em>get paid before =
the deal closes</em>. After the deal closes, your client is gone, and the h=
ostile acquirer now owns it, and he has fired all of your contacts and does=
n=E2=80=99t want to pay your bills. You send him a bill that is like =E2=80=
=9CFor fighting you off: $2 million,=E2=80=9D and he is like =E2=80=9Cwell,=
 you didn=E2=80=99t fight me off, and I didn=E2=80=99t want you to, and I=
=E2=80=99m not paying.=E2=80=9D=C2=A0</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">We <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusin=
